{"tid":151943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普政府要求46名檢察官馬上辭職","createTime":"2017-03-11T10:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T13:01:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbd765765fa04f3d68f4713d629a4c58281d3c9","tid":151943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國司法部長塞申斯突然要求46名由奧巴馬政府任命的聯邦檢察官立刻辭職。<br />\n<br />\n司法部周五發聲明宣布消息，署理司法部副部長本特正逐一致電相關檢察官，正式通知他們。<br />\n<br />\n由於事出突然，部分檢察官要透過傳媒報道才得知自己被辭退。<br />\n<br />\n在美國，新政府上台後通常都會委任新的聯邦檢察官，多位檢察官在特朗普就職後已經辭職，只餘下這46名，但在毫無預告下突然要大批檢察官立刻辭職，做法並不尋常。<br />\n<br />\n令人詫異的是紐約南區聯邦檢察官巴拉拉亦收到要求辭職通知。巴拉拉早前表示，自己已答應特朗普的挽留。他目前正監督調查紐約市長白思豪是否以政府利益換取政治捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=213706&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D213706%26refer%3Dshare&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=eddd8804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D213706%26refer%3Dshare&h=c6208f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=213706&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"eb2b331761ea504bb9438ee4800e78bc8646c4c9","tid":151943,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ba05f0c80d166f3850ea2fdd8f7dd7b645b113e","tid":151943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c68987dd84c7f90cb7bccbf6a0362daf5fca24","tid":151943,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"一朝天子一朝臣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e69129f99ec39b4ca7e37017bf8c11c3a14117c","tid":151943,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco